# surf-app

Unified multi-modal web application powering **wave.site** (website builder), **doc.surf** (team docs & tasks), and **surf.new** (public landing). Built on Rust/Axum with HTMX frontend and PostgreSQL backend.

::app[name=surf-app binary=surf-server region=sjc port=8080]

## Build

Rust 1.89, multi-stage Docker build. Migrations embedded at compile time via `sqlx::migrate!()`.

:::build[base=rust:1.89-bookworm runtime=debian:bookworm-slim edition=2024]
artifacts:
  - target/release/surf-server -> /app/surf-server
  - migrate/migrations-pg -> /app/migrate/migrations-pg
  - server/src/static -> /app/server/src/static
  - /app/uploads (created)
runtime_deps:
  - ca-certificates
  - libssl3
:::

## Database

:::database[name=surf_app_db shared_auth volume_gb=1]
migrations: 64
migration_path: migrate/migrations-pg
session_store: postgresql
connection: cloudsurf-db (retry 5x, 5s delay)
:::

## Environments

:::deploy[env=develop app=surf-app-develop machines=1 memory=256 auto_stop=suspend min_machines=0]
RUST_LOG: surf_app_server=debug,tower_http=debug
:::

:::deploy[env=staging app=surf-app-staging machines=1 memory=512 auto_stop=off min_machines=1]
RUST_LOG: surf_app_server=info,tower_http=info
:::

:::deploy[env=production app=surf-app machines=2 memory=512 auto_stop=off min_machines=2 strategy=rolling]
RUST_LOG: surf_app_server=info,tower_http=info
:::

## Health & Concurrency

:::health[path=/healthz method=GET grace=15s interval=30s timeout=5s]
:::

:::concurrency[type=requests hard_limit=250 soft_limit=200 force_https]
:::

